Fix paragliding card showing lake wind instead of FPS station data

The TodayHero activity cards used the selected lake's wind speed
for all activities, causing paragliding to show "1 mph TOO LIGHT"
while the paragliding forecast correctly showed "13 mph 95%".

Now passes FPS and UTALP station data to TodayHero and uses
those stations specifically for the paragliding verdict card.
